author: Reuters
title: DIARY - Today in Washington - Sept 25
text:
ALL TIMES IN EDT/GMT
The Commerce Dept. issues Building Permit Revisions for August.
The Bureau of Labor Statistics releases a strike report for September.
0830/1230: The Commerce Dept. issues Final (3rd estimate) U.S. Q2 Gross Domestic Product and revised (2nd estimate) U.S. Q2 Corporate Profits.
1500/1900: The USDA issues quarterly Hog and Pig Inventory.
